{"tid":1322133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日連登文宣部開始分化警察 星期日非常危險了","createTime":"2019-07-16T00:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T00:45:16.000Z","uid":82845,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"24f695c505b0dcf42382ea254a73b611a3fccbcf","tid":1322133,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:42:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28369841&amp;utm_source=copy&amp;utm_campaign=ios&amp;utm_medium=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D28369841%26utm_source%3Dcopy%26utm_campaign%3Dios%26utm_medium%3Dshare&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXpE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=82412e6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28369841&amp;utm_source=copy&amp;utm_campaign=ios&amp;utm_medium=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日經過流膿牆，見到大量標語矛頭指向警隊管理層，話管理層失當導致前線警員受傷云云.....香討亦看到大量相關留言，可見到暴徒文宣部開始吹風，意圖分化警隊內部。<br />\n0<br />\n背後原因除了針對警隊高層外，我最最最担心的是暴徒正計劃星期日要再傷害警員，甚至要殺警。<br />\n<br />\n如果星期日真係有警察嚴重受傷，甚至死亡的話，毒媒大可說成警方部署失當，導致警員死亡，將責任推落警方高層頭上，而殺人犯只係受警察煽動，或是政府迫佢地等等，將視線轉移。<br />\n<br />\n所以我認為此計甚毒，警察的人身安全非常受威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香討文宣部割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明示威行動佔大部有份參與"},{"pid":"7b9a427a113c3ad2466ef4675800319ff3662989","tid":1322133,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:45:16.000Z","msg":"［建制議員應總辭］39嘆冷氣逗人工議員拎光環譴責暴力，何君堯關鍵缺席聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}